_:N539ed1c7a64e483d9e9c3eda13dad9fb <http://schema.org/description> "This first Modern Slavery Statement sets out steps DWP has taken to understand where slavery could occur in its supply chains and actions to mitigate and manage this, to help ensure that taxpayers’ money does not inadvertently fund this cruel and criminal activity." .
